撚振奮人心"},{"pid":"5b6f33d9525c8c34171996d43ec340dd4746e10e","tid":1437820,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e455d875628878b4d280a168f42a03987be757f7","tid":1437820,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54dc2f6f6969a92584dec9c74bf485a877591356","tid":1437820,"uid":143987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"721聽到好多人叫<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n好撚振奮人心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f057d9b14522d0fc13f595691c449a886d591109","tid":1437820,"uid":213048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edc96953901566a97b30b82b2868ee7c6f0daa4","tid":1437820,"uid":227433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:13:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22518509ab9edf2a06d1e157a051c1914027da63","tid":1437820,"uid":92398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:19:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d237594b435c50b20b3f98611adf43e0ccaa0e87","tid":1437820,"uid":145979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"其實想講好耐，呢個口照最大嘅用途係:增加返香港人嘅身分凝聚力<br />\n<br />\n由689條仆街上場後，日日話香港呢到唔得呢樣唔掂，深圳上海超越香港，再加埋一眾媒體嘅吹捧，即使你唔信呢件，但係成個社會嘅氛圍都係充斥住香港邊緣化呢種論調。香港嘅地位係難以取替，但已經搖搖欲墜，硬件有產業單一化，軟件有廣東話不斷被取締，種種劣幣驅逐良幣令到今時今日咁嘅地步。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，因為歷史原因，香港一直比人拋黎拋去，亦因為鄰國歷年來的政權不穩政制敗壞，不斷有大量外來人口加入香港，令到香港變成無根地，個個只係以生計為主，所以上幾代嘅人意想裏面完全無以香港為主呢個心態去做野，更加唔洗講中共每日派150，不斷人口清洗，政策嘅嚴重偏側再加上控制議會內外，由早期嘅同鄉會到近期嘅愛國團體，不斷瓜分政府資源去穩維。<br />\n<br />\n其實對方一早打住一家人嘅旗號黎玩種族主義，所以香港人真係急需一個身分認同，以後好多事解釋起上黎就方便好多。"},{"pid":"28a03ff255e601d9468dc5ad15c1fb07ec723713","tid":1437820,"uid":266161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:07:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"21a31759d3b81deadf5420935ef49ea06fcf4fda","tid":1437820,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d458f3fd352dd35089298ba8ee878c7d45dd0eec","tid":1437820,"uid":301214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T22:53:23.000Z","msg":"推，說中了心聲"},{"pid":"298229428db4a332ad28ba415f804e862a4bcfd1","tid":1437820,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}